===Noun===
'''[[Montezuma]]’s [[revenge]]''' or '''[[Moctezuma]]’s [[revenge]]'''

# A term given to [[diarrhea]] experienced by tourists after drinking water or eating food in [[Mexico]] as a result of a [[bacteria]] [[strain]] to which [[native]] Mexicans are [[immune]]. So named for the supposed last native ruler of the area before it was conquered by the Spanish.

